INDICATOR_NAME: Agricultural raw materials imports (% of merchandise imports)
SOURCE_NOTE: Agricultural raw materials comprise SITC section 2 (crude materials except fuels) excluding divisions 22, 27 (crude fertilizers and minerals excluding coal, petroleum, and precious stones), and 28 (metalliferous ores and scrap).
SOURCE_ORGANIZATION: World Bank staff estimates from the Comtrade database maintained by the United Nations Statistics Division.
